{"tid":2442783,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"政治笑話","createTime":"2021-03-11T14:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T01:50:55.000Z","uid":229502,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"537f01890c0958c714a0051769c93552b970b43e","tid":2442783,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"1. 你知道嗎？在香港人的眼中，有時候半年比一年過得更慢<br />\n<br />\n2.二戰後，前往蘇聯/俄羅斯的客機上，如果有人在上機時已經穿了防寒衣服，那麼他有八成機會是德國人<br />\n<br />\n3.有些人以正當的概念、不理性的言語、無差別的暴力，將思想散揚開去。其實大部分國家都是這樣，但他們不會毫無目標地攻擊任何人。<br />\n<br />\n4.甲說年輕人在戰場上，老年人卻圍着桌子說廢話。丁說老年人漏夜討論戰況時，年輕人正在休息。乙說年輕人連甚麼時候會死也不知道，老年人卻在開宴會。丙說人人都會死，不要再討論了。然後當敵人大敗我方時，首都被人轟炸。甲乙丙丁都死了。在郊外住的戊說老年人指揮不好，年輕人會死。年輕人打得不好，老年人會死。其實這五個人都沒有考慮所有方面。<br />\n<br />\n5.樓主是政治白痴，這整個po就是一個政治笑話。"},{"pid":"a00e6c6dd67fb1dea85254ef61c7f2ce19629a8c","tid":2442783,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db56f2b6021368e60bed654589cab8a1168b468","tid":2442783,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52bf178d0ef0ea4426f659336e0e0abcc470f9e","tid":2442783,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3aaf64c535690570f7583c6965e0d1e5013a2c","tid":2442783,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a00e6c6dd67fb1dea85254ef6